{"tid":24554,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[葡萄]見到有個港女拎BC留學日本","createTime":"2016-12-05T15:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T10:43:19.000Z","uid":12261,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eba42dbe30b203d94c95ac291b750f031118c4c3","tid":24554,"uid":12261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:05:07.000Z","msg":"無意中睇到呢個blog<br />\n<a href=\"http://thlhelen.blogspot.hk/2014/02/blog-post_22.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthlhelen.blogspot.hk%2F2014%2F02%2Fblog-post_22.html%3Fm%3D1&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=16859424\" target=\"_blank\">http://thlhelen.blogspot.hk/2014/02/blog-post_22.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-oLl8SJdlQyY/UwiwDCwp6lI/AAAAAAAAAdo/leGY-RZK_f0/s1600/2014-02-21+15.10.21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-oLl8SJdlQyY%2FUwiwDCwp6lI%2FAAAAAAAAAdo%2FleGY-RZK_f0%2Fs1600%2F2014-02-21%2B15.10.21.jpg&h=c7429514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，辦簽證時發生了小插曲－－<br />\n<br />\n職員：（望了望我的護照，發現新大陸）咦？這不是ＢＮＯ來的！<br />\n我：（茫然）喔，對哦 <br />\n職員：（抓包）你是不是向學校報錯了國籍？<br />\n我： 我跟學校說我是British Citizen啊，（指著在留資格認定証明書上的國籍）這不就寫著英國．香港嗎？（茫然）<br />\n職員：英國．香港是指ＢＮＯ啊，你的英籍護照應該寫英國，不是英國．香港～<br />\n我：（茫然）呃．．．（一副嚇呆的表情） <br />\n職員：（一邊把文件夾好一邊說）我們會幫你辦妥的了，不過之後你收到任何奇怪電話都要接，因為我們會打給你啊，記著我們打結你才好來取證～～<br />\n<br />\n　　很多人都會以為英籍護照跟ＢＮＯ是一樣的，但香港人一般都是用ＢＮＯ，所以你說英籍別人都會以為是ＢＮＯ／口＼我還是去申請一本香港護照好了，好像比較方便。<br />\n__________________<br />\n<br />\n唔知佢真心含住金匙出世身在福中不知福定係BC撚都要曬命既港女<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇呢種人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好唔好叫佢返英國住？<br />\n<br />\n利申 BNO 有好幾個朋友親戚都係BC"},{"pid":"d86efdfd1f1680b593b11dd8803f3d857d1ae795","tid":24554,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:07:49.000Z","msg":"睇個樣似係有錢女"},{"pid":"12ca40d0a2dfe74e46d592838f8c6e4cd8b700b8","tid":24554,"uid":12261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:08:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇個樣似係有錢女</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去日本留學周圍玩 可以點冇錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 中產 一d 都唔需要葡萄佢"},{"pid":"1914d0992d49ab6140f9961160f796e28867f5cc","tid":24554,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:11:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇個樣似係有錢女</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去日本留學周圍玩 可以點冇錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 中產 一d 都唔需要葡萄佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識得有人唔係好有錢都去日本讀書<br />\n父廚房 母樓面"},{"pid":"58f23684323eb65f3d39114003aed725fe357e33","tid":24554,"uid":12261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:14:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇個樣似係有錢女</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去日本留學周圍玩 可以點冇錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 中產 一d 都唔需要葡萄佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識得有人唔係好有錢都去日本讀書<br />\n父廚房 母樓面</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n重點係有錢嗎日本周圍吃喝玩樂生活無憂<br />\n睇下佢其他blog post"},{"pid":"dfcca843a447192bf373915f4da7f550104e1ae7","tid":24554,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇個樣似係有錢女</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去日本留學周圍玩 可以點冇錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 中產 一d 都唔需要葡萄佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識得有人唔係好有錢都去日本讀書<br />\n父廚房 母樓面</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n重點係有錢嗎日本周圍吃喝玩樂生活無憂<br />\n睇下佢其他blog post</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲以為而家仲有人用blog<br />\n原來14年"},{"pid":"07aa57c68790f735fc31eff3c5a63cb4619ef8bb","tid":24554,"uid":26037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:16:01.000Z","msg":"唔明點解揀得錯<br />\n拎BC 咪填英國<br />\n拎BNO 咪填香港 (英國) / 英國國民 (海外)<br />\n拎火車頭咪填 香港 (中國) / 香港<br />\n<br />\n望住自己本護照個國籍欄都唔識填?"},{"pid":"0829c2037d5edc1bb13763a13137e1a9cd89e94b","tid":24554,"uid":12261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:18:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔明點解揀得錯<br />\n拎BC 咪填英國<br />\n拎BNO 咪填香港 (英國) / 英國國民 (海外)<br />\n拎火車頭咪填 香港 (中國) / 香港<br />\n<br />\n望住自己本護照個國籍欄都唔識填?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曬梗命都睇唔明？<br />\n仲話british passport冇咁好用想申請特區喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc0827c5177b2dee1cd9a46a4c3b7d3cf711530","tid":24554,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:28:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d1f338a47b3b25ab13f2e65e1b4023a90f008d4","tid":24554,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:29:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1f25d6a6cb169c459ef9c097776c362c3e8bf7c","tid":24554,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:29:54.000Z","msg":"如果條友係揸日本護照去英國留學我就葡萄<br />\n<br />\n佢喺日本留學唔代表喺日本搵到工，佢去英國人地又未必請佢/搵到工，淨番香港俾佢喺班BNO或者特衰面前曬命<br />\n<br />\n利申：冇BC但唔葡萄"},{"pid":"fe3ca30dcfc1bb272752b4a1d1d312754418d6f3","tid":24554,"uid":12261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:33:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔明點解揀得錯<br />\n拎BC 咪填英國<br />\n拎BNO 咪填香港 (英國) / 英國國民 (海外)<br />\n拎火車頭咪填 香港 (中國) / 香港<br />\n<br />\n望住自己本護照個國籍欄都唔識填?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曬梗命都睇唔明？<br />\n仲話british passport冇咁好用想申請特區喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好心你班戇尻仔唔好諗到人咁有計算啦　小朋友來咖咋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n92年人 14年寫<br />\n22歲<br />\n小朋友？<br />\n今年都做得人地老母了<br />\n如果都仲寫d 咁既blog 我真係好羨慕佢<br />\n有一個家庭俾到佢咁好既條件繼續天真落去<br />\n最重要係暴殄天物/得罪一班得唔到英國公民權利既英籍港人<br />\n再利申 唔支持歸英"},{"pid":"ab592f938b247d780b4057bfe2a4129ad0d363b6","tid":24554,"uid":26037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:33:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔明點解揀得錯<br />\n拎BC 咪填英國<br />\n拎BNO 咪填香港 (英國) / 英國國民 (海外)<br />\n拎火車頭咪填 香港 (中國) / 香港<br />\n<br />\n望住自己本護照個國籍欄都唔識填?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曬梗命都睇唔明？<br />\n仲話british passport冇咁好用想申請特區喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔係自己努力拎返黎既野<br />\n有乜好曬? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做人做到要用一個身分打飛機 <br />\n咁佢都幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 窮撚 無BNO/BC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20103d7428f7139e2f04b899adacb7ad4b1a90db","tid":24554,"uid":26037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:34:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔明點解揀得錯<br />\n拎BC 咪填英國<br />\n拎BNO 咪填香港 (英國) / 英國國民 (海外)<br />\n拎火車頭咪填 香港 (中國) / 香港<br />\n<br />\n望住自己本護照個國籍欄都唔識填?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曬梗命都睇唔明？<br />\n仲話british passport冇咁好用想申請特區喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔係自己努力拎返黎既野<br />\n有乜好曬? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做人做到要用一個身分打飛機 <br />\n咁佢都幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 窮撚 無BNO/BC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBTW 唔排除佢真係以為 BC + HKID = 香港 (英國) 既"},{"pid":"fec113be8d150e2ca6640e58ac194a7a61677077","tid":24554,"uid":12261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:36:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔明點解揀得錯<br />\n拎BC 咪填英國<br />\n拎BNO 咪填香港 (英國) / 英國國民 (海外)<br />\n拎火車頭咪填 香港 (中國) / 香港<br />\n<br />\n望住自己本護照個國籍欄都唔識填?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曬梗命都睇唔明？<br />\n仲話british passport冇咁好用想申請特區喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔係自己努力拎返